data.description: Stop scrolling, this is the one! Check out this 3 bed 2 bath brick home on almost 4 acres! This gorgeous property is just outside of Whitney city limits and only 3 miles from lake Whitney. Inside you will find an updated kitchen and fresh paint throughout. The roof was replaced in July of 2023 and the HVAC was replaced in 2020. There is also a generous sized 30x24 detached garage and the property is fenced on 3 sides.
